# Cursor Rules for Amplify Gen2 Sample Project

## Project Overview
This is an AWS Amplify Gen2 sample project using Node.js and Alpine Linux in a dev container.

## Development Guidelines
- Use Node.js 20
- Follow ESLint and Prettier configurations
- Use TypeScript for type safety
- Follow AWS Amplify Gen2 best practices

## File Structure
- `.devcontainer/` - Dev container configuration
- `src/` - Source code
- `amplify/` - Amplify configuration files

## Common Commands
- `npm install` - Install dependencies
- `npm run dev` - Start development server
- `amplify push` - Deploy changes to AWS 